khulafah","tag-companions-sahaba","tag-leadership-imamah","tag-marriage-al-nikah","tag-surah-al-tahreem","tag-umar-ibn-al-khattab"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-bj8","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":38968,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/03\/02\/ali-testifies-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":43470,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Ali testifies for Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Abdu Khayr reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cShall I not inform you of the best from this nation after its Prophet? It is Abu Bakr, and the best after him is Umar. Then, Allah will place goodness wherever He wishes.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 922 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11080,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/ali-best-ummah-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":43470,"position":1},"title":"Ali on Caliphs: Best companions are Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Juhayfah reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you about the best of this nation after its Prophet? It is Abu Bakr and Umar.\" Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 878 Grade\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u062c\u064f\u062d\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11077,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/after-prophet-khulafah-rashidun\/","url_meta":{"origin":43470,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: After the Prophet, follow Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: We were sitting with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cI surely do not know how much longer I will remain with you. After me, follow these two,\u201d and the Prophet pointed to Abu Bakr and Umar. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3663 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43679,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/14\/prophet-always-with-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":43470,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: The Prophet always with Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Umar was placed upon his bier as the people surrounded him, supplicated for him, and performed the funeral prayer over him before he was taken away. I was there, and nothing else held my attention but a man putting his hand on my shoulder. It was Ali,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21345,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/12\/17\/ata-on-shubuhat-huded\/","url_meta":{"origin":43470,"position":4},"title":"\u2018Ata on Doubts: Caliphs order accused to deny his crime","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 17, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ata reported: Those who came before would be presented with someone accused of theft and they would say, \u201cHave you stolen? Say no.\u201d I do not know who did so except Abu Bakr and Umar. Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 28014 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064d \u064a\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43710,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/15\/best-ummah-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":43470,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Best of Ummah are Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 15, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: In the lifetime of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while his companions were numerous, we preferred Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman, then we would remain silent. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 4626 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut Imam Ahmad commented, \u201cThe best of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u063